# Prefer shadcn UI components

- For UI implementation, prefer existing components from `shadcn/ui` first.
- Before creating a new custom UI component, check whether an equivalent `shadcn` component exists and can be adapted.
- Reuse project wrapper components built on top of `shadcn` when available.
- Build custom components only when `shadcn` does not cover the requirement or when product-specific behavior is needed.
